content: ChristopherTrimboli: Merged 4 pull requests in elizaos/eliza, highlighted by a major documentation update in #5236 (+9578/-7862 lines) and a large cleanup of CLI packages in #5237. He also opened a new proof-of-concept PR for a workflows plugin (#5299) and was active in code review, providing 13 reviews. Overall activity was focused on documentation and refactoring, with two smaller bug fixes merged as well (#5298, #5296).
